<view class="container about-page">
  <view class="about-hero">
    <view class="brand-mark">
      <text>商</text>
    </view>
    <view class="brand-copy">
      <text class="brand-title">轻量商城</text>
      <text class="brand-subtitle">面向课程设计的电商小程序示例</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-block">
    <view class="info-panel">
      <view class="panel-head">
        <text class="panel-title">项目简介</text>
      </view>
      <text class="intro-text">
        本项目围绕电商购物的核心链路展开，覆盖商品浏览、分类筛选、购物车、订单确认、地址管理和个人中心等模块。页面设计以清晰、克制和可操作为主，优先保证课设场景中的功能闭环。
      </text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-block">
    <view class="info-panel">
      <view class="panel-head">
        <text class="panel-title">服务承诺</text>
      </view>
      <block wx:for="{{commitments}}" wx:key="*this">
        <view class="list-row">
          <view class="row-dot"></view>
          <text class="row-text">{{item}}</text>
        </view>
      </block>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-block">
    <view class="info-panel">
      <view class="panel-head">
        <text class="panel-title">联系与版本</text>
      </view>
      <block wx:for="{{contacts}}" wx:key="label">
        <view class="meta-row">
          <text class="meta-label">{{item.label}}</text>
          <text class="meta-value">{{item.value}}</text>
        </view>
      </block>
      <view class="meta-row">
        <text class="meta-label">当前版本</text>
        <text class="meta-value">v{{version}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-block">
    <button class="contact-btn" open-type="contact" hover-class="active-feedback">联系客服</button>
  </view>

  <view class="safe-bottom"></view>
</view>
